<h1>Privacy Policy — COTW Wild Life</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 11/30/2025</p>

<p>The <strong>COTW Wild Life</strong> application respects user privacy and is committed to ensuring that no personal information is collected, used, or shared.</p>

<h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
<p>The application does <strong>not</strong> collect, store, transmit, or share any personal user data. This includes, but is not limited to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Name, email, or phone number</li>
    <li>Login credentials</li>
    <li>Location data</li>
    <li>Personal files</li>
    <li>Device information</li>
    <li>Unique identifiers</li>
    <li>Sensitive data</li>
</ul>
<p>No data is sent to external servers or stored in the cloud.</p>

<h2>2. Permissions</h2>
<p>The application does not request any special permissions beyond those required for its standard functionality. The app does <strong>not</strong> access:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Internet</li>
    <li>Location</li>
    <li>Microphone</li>
    <li>Personal files</li>
    <li>Contacts</li>
    <li>Calendar</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Local Storage</h2>
<p>Some information may be stored locally on the device, such as:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Language preferences</li>
    <li>App configuration settings</li>
</ul>
<p>This data never leaves the user's device.</p>

<h2>4. Children</h2>
<p>The application is suitable for all ages. Since no data is collected, the app complies with <strong>LGPD</strong> (Brazil), <strong>GDPR</strong> (Europe), and general child protection guidelines.</p>

<h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
<p>No information of any kind is shared with third parties.</p>

<h2>6. Security</h2>
<p>Because <strong>COTW Wild Life</strong> does not collect or transmit personal data, there is no risk of exposure or leakage of user information.</p>

<h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>This policy may be updated to reflect improvements in the application. Whenever changes occur, the latest version will always be available on this page.</p>

<h2>8. Contact</h2>
<p>If you have questions or requests related to privacy, please contact:</p>
<p><strong>Email:</strong> reviloude.gamer@gmail.com</p>

